var hello = 'hello';
var world = 'world';
var mark = '!';
var options = {
silent: true
};
function greet(options, first, second){
if (options.silent){
return '...';
}
var local = [first, second, mark].join(' ');
return local
}
greet = greet.bind(null, options);
['Alice', 'John'].forEach(function(name){
console.log(name, 'said:', greet(hello, world));
})
